<template>
  <nav>
    <button  @click="changemode">Change Theme</button>
  </nav>
</template>

<script>
import { mapState } from 'vuex'
export default {
  name:'PortfolioNavbar',
    methods:{
        changemode(){
            this.$store.commit('CHANGEMODE')
        }
    },
    computed:{
        ...mapState(['theme'])
    }
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
